      <body>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e203" who="SPK0" start="T30" end="T33">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e203">I mean did you think: <anchor synch="T3"/>"Good God <anchor synch="T4"/>this/ <anchor synch="T5"/>this is the guy, <anchor synch="T31"/>this is the girl I'm gonna get married to and live the rest of my life with?" <anchor synch="T32"/>((0,4s)) David? </u>
            <spanGrp type="c">
               <span from="T3" to="T32">Reported speech</span>
            </spanGrp>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T30" to="T3">Ich meine, dachtest Du: </span>
               <span from="T3" to="T4">"Lieber Gott, </span>
               <span from="T4" to="T5">das/ </span>
               <span from="T5" to="T31">das ist der Kerl, </span>
               <span from="T31" to="T32">das ist das Mädchen das ich heiraten werde und mit dem ich den Rest meines Lebens verbringe?" </span>
               <span from="T32" to="T33">((0,4s)) David? </span>
            </spanGrp>
            <spanGrp type="df">
               <span from="T4" to="T5">TROUBLE</span>
            </spanGrp>
         </annotationBlock>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e305" who="SPK2" start="T33" end="T34">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e305">I felt that, yeah. </u>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T33" to="T34">Ich habe das gefühlt, ja. </span>
            </spanGrp>
         </annotationBlock>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e222" who="SPK0" start="T34" end="T2">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e222">Did you? </u>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T34" to="T2">Hast Du? </span>
            </spanGrp>
         </annotationBlock>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e308" who="SPK2" start="T2" end="T36">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e308">Definitely. <anchor synch="T35"/>You did I hope, didn't you? </u>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T2" to="T35">Definitiv. </span>
               <span from="T35" to="T36">Du auch, hoffe ich, oder? </span>
            </spanGrp>
         </annotationBlock>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e275" who="SPK1" start="T36" end="T38">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e275">((0,3s)) Yeah. <anchor synch="T37"/>((laughing))</u>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T36" to="T37">((0,3s)) Ja. </span>
               <span from="T37" to="T38">((lacht)) </span>
            </spanGrp>
         </annotationBlock>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e225" who="SPK0" start="T37" end="T40">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e225">((laughing)) <anchor synch="T38"/>Was <anchor synch="T39"/>it really like that? </u>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T37" to="T38">((lacht)) </span>
               <span from="T38" to="T40">War es wirklich so? </span>
            </spanGrp>
         </annotationBlock>
         <annotationBlock xml:id="ab_d2e314" who="SPK2" start="T37" end="T46">
            <u xml:id="u_d2e314">((laughing)) <anchor synch="T38"/>Yeah. <anchor synch="T39"/>Yeah, yeah, <anchor synch="T6"/>I was/ I was/ <anchor synch="T40"/>it was definitely. <anchor synch="T41"/>((0,3s)) As soon as <anchor synch="T42"/>I see <anchor synch="T43"/>her. <anchor synch="T44"/>You know, I didn't even have to meet her. <anchor synch="T45"/>I seen her on the telly and I just wanted to meet her. </u>
            <spanGrp type="de">
               <span from="T37" to="T38">((lacht)) </span>
               <span from="T38" to="T39">Ja. </span>
               <span from="T39" to="T6">Ja, ja, </span>
               <span from="T6" to="T40">ich war/ ich war/ </span>
               <span from="T40" to="T41">es war definitiv so. </span>
               <span from="T41" to="T44">Sobald ich sie gesehen habe. </span>
               <span from="T44" to="T45">Weißt Du, ich musste sie noch nicht mal treffen. </span>
               <span from="T45" to="T46">Ich habe sie im Fernsehen gesehen und ich wollte sie einfach treffen. </span>
            </spanGrp>
